## üöÄ Deployment Strategy

### Phase 1: Development on Lovable.dev

**Why Lovable.dev first:**
- ‚úÖ **Instant deployment** from GitHub
- ‚úÖ **Built for full-stack apps** like NeuroTunes Elite
- ‚úÖ **Free tier** perfect for testing
- ‚úÖ **Easy environment management**
- ‚úÖ **Automatic HTTPS** and CDN

**Lovable.dev Setup:**

1. **Push to GitHub:**
   ```bash
   git init
   git add .
   git commit -m "Initial NeuroTunes Elite stack"
   git branch -M main
   git remote add origin https://github.com/yourusername/neurotunes-elite
   git push -u origin main
   ```

2. **Connect to Lovable:**
   - Go to [lovable.dev](https://lovable.dev)
   - Click "Deploy from GitHub"
   - Select your NeuroTunes repository
   - Lovable auto-detects the config

3. **Configure Environment:**
   ```bash
   # In Lovable dashboard ‚Üí Environment Variables
   VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...
   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...
   NODE_ENV=production
   ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://your-app.lovable.dev
   ```

4. **Deploy & Test:**
   - Auto-deploys on every GitHub push
   - Test at: `https://your-app.lovable.dev`
   - Check health: `https://your-app.lovable.dev/api/health`

### Phase 2: Production on Railway

**Why Railway for production:**
- ‚úÖ **Enterprise-grade infrastructure**
- ‚úÖ **Auto-scaling** for traffic spikes
- ‚úÖ **Global edge network**
- ‚úÖ **Database add-ons** (if you need Redis/PostgreSQL)
- ‚úÖ **Custom domains** with SSL
- ‚úÖ **Better monitoring** and logs

**Railway Setup:**

1. **Connect Repository:**
   - Go to [railway.app](https://railway.app)
   - "Deploy from GitHub"
   - Select NeuroTunes repository

2. **Environment Variables:**
   ```bash
   # In Railway dashboard ‚Üí Variables
   VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...
   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...
   NODE_ENV=production
   PORT=$PORT
   ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://your-domain.com,https://neurotunes-elite.railway.app
   RAILWAY_STATIC_URL=https://neurotunes-elite.railway.app
   ```

3. **Custom Domain:**
   - Railway dashboard ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Custom Domain
   - Add your domain: `neurotunes-elite.com`
   - Configure DNS: `CNAME ‚Üí your-app.railway.app`

4. **Monitoring Setup:**
   ```bash
   # Railway automatically provides:
   # - Application logs
   # - Metrics dashboard  
   # - Uptime monitoring
   # - Performance insights
   ```

### Platform Comparison

| Feature | Lovable.dev | Railway |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Purpose** | Development & Testing | Production |
| **Deployment Speed** | ‚ö° Instant | ‚ö° Fast |
| **Free Tier** | ‚úÖ Generous | ‚úÖ Good |
| **Custom Domains** | ‚úÖ Yes | ‚úÖ Yes + SSL |
| **Auto-scaling** | ‚ùå Limited | ‚úÖ Yes |
| **Monitoring** | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê Basic | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê Advanced |
| **Best For** | MVP, Testing | Production, Scale |

