## üéµ Adding Your Music Files

### Method 1: Supabase Dashboard
1. Go to Storage ‚Üí neurotunes-music
2. Create folders: `frequency-bands/delta/`, `alpha/`, etc.
3. Upload your music files
4. Update database with file paths

### Method 2: Upload Component (Future Feature)
```typescript
// Add this to your app later
const uploadTrack = async (file: File, metadata: any) => {
  const path = `frequency-bands/${metadata.frequency_band}/${file.name}`
  
  // Upload to Supabase
  const { data, error } = await supabase.storage
    .from('neurotunes-music')
    .upload(path, file)
  
  if (!error) {
    // Add to database
    await supabase.from('music_tracks').insert({
      ...metadata,
      file_path: path,
      upload_status: 'completed'
    })
  }
}
```

